# ==========================================================================
# This repository publishes ANALYSIS SCRIPTS ONLY.
#
# Strategy: ignore everything at the top level by default, then explicitly
# "un-ignore" (!) the script and documentation files we DO want to publish.
# Raw data, intermediate files, figures, outputs, and manuscripts stay local
# and are never uploaded to GitHub.
# ==========================================================================

# 1. Ignore everything in the project root by default.
/*

# 2. ...but keep these files:
!.gitignore
!README.md
!LICENSE
!*.Rmd
!*.R
!*.Rproj

# Never commit R session/history artifacts even if they appear.
.Rhistory
.RData
.RDataTmp
.Rproj.user/
